snippet.title: Men of War II - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Experience warfare like never before! Men of War II, the anticipated sequel to the acclaimed RTS franchise is here with all-new units, locations, campaigns, and game modes, combined with the series’ trademark historical accuracy and action-filled gameplay on Eastern and Western Fronts of WWII.

Coming on PC - WISHLIST NOW!
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1128860/Men_of_War_II/
Epic Games Store: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/men-of-war-ii-171a7e

Join the Men of War II official discord: https://discord.gg/VszFwDPKTy
